[Description]
    The scripts in this folder are for packing offline installation package. 

[Usage]
First time setup
    1. Prepare a VM or physical machine installed a clean Ubuntu 12.04 server.
    2. ./1st_config_environment.sh
    
First build package
    1. sudo ./build_gw_package.sh full <build_num>
        Example: sudo ./build_gw_package.sh full 0093

Fast rebuild (already ran full build)
    1. sudo ./build_gw_package.sh fast <build_num>
        Example: sudo ./build_gw_package.sh fast 0093
